quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Sad (This is name of a letter of the Arabic alphabet, and only Allah knows its meaning here) and (by) the Qur'an comprising the Remembrance"
  38,2,"No indeed, (but) the ones who have disbelieved are in might and opposition"
  38,3,"How many a generation We caused to perish even before them, yet they called out, while time had lapsed for shirking (their doom)"
  38,4,"And they wonder that a warner has come to them from among them, and the disbelievers have said, \"This is a sorcerer, a (great) liar"
  38,5,Has he made the gods one God? Surely this is indeed a most wondrous thing
  38,6,"And the chiefs among them went off, (saying), \"Go on! (Or: March on!) And endure (patiently) with your gods; surely this indeed is a thing willfully (designed)"
  38,7,In no way did we hear of this in the last creed; decidedly this is nothing except a made-up device
  38,8,"Has the Remembrance been sent down on him from among us?\" No indeed, (but) they are in doubt of My Remembrance; no indeed (but) they have not as yet tasted My torment"
  38,9,"Or even do they have in their presence the treasuries of your Lord's mercy, The Ever-Mighty, Superb Bestower"
  38,10,Or even does the kingdom of the heavens and the earth and whatever is between them belong to them? Then let them ascend the means
  38,11,A very host of the (allied) parties is routed from these
  38,12,"The people of Nuh, (Noah) and c?d, and Firaawn, (Pharaoh) owner of the bulwarks, cried lies before them"
  38,13,"And Thamud, and the people of Lut (Lot) and the companions of the Thicket; those were the (allied) parties"
  38,14,"Decidedly not one but cried lies to the Messengers, so My punishment came true"
  38,15,And in no way are these looking for anything except one Shout; in no way is there any recovery from it
  38,16,"And they have said, \"Our Lord, hasten (quickly) to us our sentence before the Day of Reckoning"